In [[mathematics]], '''Raynaud's isogeny theorem''', proved by {{harvs|txt|last=Raynaud|year=1985|authorlink=Michel Raynaud}}, relates the [[Faltings height]]s of two isogeneous [[elliptic curve]]s.

